data.description: ALL OF THE BIG TICKET ITEMS HAVE BEEN TAKEN CARE OF.  Just completed Exterior painting of entire home.  Recently installed new $11,000 HVAC System.  Installation of New Hot Water Heater.   New flooring throughout. Spacious and private split floor plan. High Ceilings throughout.  4 Bedrooms, 2 baths,  Formal living room.  Family room open to Kitchen and Dining Room.  Kitchen has Bar perfect for casual meals, Large Pantry. Master Bedroom has Walk-in Closet.  Master Bath has dual vanities, standalone tub and separate shower Separate Water Closet for more privacy.  Ceiling fans in all rooms including the very large screened lanai which has more than ample room for entertaining. House has completely fenced back yard, and backs up to Nature so that you will never have any rear neighbors.  The community of Bahia Lakes offers a swimming pool, playground, and walking trails.  Close to I-75 and 41 making it convenient to Tampa and St Petersburg. SEE REALTOR ONLY REMARKS FOR ADDITIONAL IMPORTANT INFORMATION.
